column2: select   s.bestobjid, s.ra, s.dec, if(s.instrument=&&&,s.z,s.z_noqso) as z, if(s.instrument=&&&,s.zerr,s.zerr_noqso) as zerr,   g.*   into mydb.galspecline_all_DR1#    from    galSpecLine g, specobj s    where   g.specobjid = s.specobjid   and if(s.instrument=&&&,s.class,s.class_noqso) = &&&
